---
/**
 * Homepage (Redesign)
 * Tight funnel, monospace utilitarian + editorial warmth.
 */
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import EmailSignup from '../components/EmailSignup.astro';
import SocialLinks from '../components/SocialLinks.astro';
import Logo from '../components/Logo.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Channel47 — building an autonomous Google Ads agent"
  description="Media buyer building an open-source AI agent that manages Google Ads like a senior buyer — audits, fixes, pacing, queries — and sharing the build in public."
>
  <main class="home">
    <div class="home__container">
      <header class="home__hero" data-section="hero" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="1">
        <p class="home__overline">BUILDING IN PUBLIC</p>
        <h1 class="home__headline">Stop clicking. Start supervising.</h1>
        <p class="home__subhead">
          I’m a media buyer building an open-source AI agent that manages Google Ads the way a senior buyer would — audits, fixes, pacing, queries, the whole loop. So you can stop doing the same 50 tasks every Monday and start running your book like an operator.
        </p>
        <div class="home__hero-cta">
          <a class="home__cta" href="#signup">Get the build notes</a>
          <p class="home__cta-note">
            Working automations, prompt templates, and real results as I ship them. No fluff.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <hr class="divider" aria-hidden="true" />

      <section class="home__section" data-section="mission" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="2">
        <p class="home__kicker">WHY THIS EXISTS</p>
        <div class="home__prose">
          <p>
            I manage 25+ accounts across multiple MCCs. The job isn’t strategy most days — it’s the same checklist on repeat.
          </p>
          <ul class="home__list">
            <li>Check pacing.</li>
            <li>Pull search terms.</li>
            <li>Pause the obvious waste.</li>
            <li>Fix extensions.</li>
            <li>Flag the budget that’s about to blow.</li>
            <li>Write the same audit you wrote last Tuesday.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            I started automating pieces of it with a Claude Code plugin.
          </p>
          <div class="home__callout">
            <p>
              One script caught a negative keyword gap that was burning ~$3K/month across two accounts.
            </p>
            <p>
              Another flagged a pacing issue 4 days before the client would’ve noticed.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            That’s when it clicked: these aren’t one-off scripts. This is an agent.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="home__section" data-section="build" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="3">
        <p class="home__kicker">WHAT IT ACTUALLY DOES</p>
        <div class="home__prose">
          <p class="home__loop">
            <span class="home__loop-label">Loop:</span>
            <span class="home__loop-value">audit → decide → execute → report</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            The agent runs a loop — audit, decide, execute, report — with guardrails so you approve changes instead of living in the UI.
          </p>
          <p>
            In practice, that means:
          </p>
          <ul class="home__feature-list">
            <li>
              <strong>It catches the expensive miss you’re too busy to find.</strong>
              The broad match keyword quietly spending $180/day on garbage queries. The campaign that paced out Tuesday but nobody noticed until Friday.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>It does the Monday morning work before Monday morning.</strong>
              Search term reports. Negative keyword builds. Extension gaps. RSA performance flags. The stuff you know matters but never gets prioritized because a client Slack just came in.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>It explains itself in plain English.</strong>
              Not a black box. Every change comes with reasoning you can read, approve, or override. You stay in control — you just stop doing the grunt work.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            I’m building it on top of skills and connectors I’ve already battle-tested on real accounts, pushing toward real autonomy one step at a time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="home__section" data-section="status" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="4">
        <p class="home__kicker">WHERE IT STANDS</p>
        <div class="home__prose">
          <p>
            This isn’t vaporware. The plugin that became the foundation already runs in production on my accounts.
          </p>
          <p>
            I’m building the full agent in public — code on GitHub, progress on Substack, decisions and dead ends included.
          </p>
          <p>
            When it’s ready, it ships open-source. Any media buyer can run it on their own accounts, their own infrastructure, no vendor lock-in.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="home__section home__signup" id="signup" data-section="signup" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="5">
        <p class="home__kicker">GET BUILD NOTES</p>
        <p class="home__signup-title">Get build notes.</p>
        <p class="home__signup-body">
          Short emails when something real ships. You’ll get the working pieces as I build them — prompt templates, automation scripts, and the architecture decisions behind an agent that actually touches live ad accounts.
        </p>
        <p class="home__signup-body">
          If you manage Google Ads and you’ve ever thought “I shouldn’t be the one doing this” — this is the build to follow.
        </p>
        <ul class="home__list home__signup-list">
          <li>Working automations and scripts.</li>
          <li>Prompt templates and playbooks.</li>
          <li>Architecture decisions (and dead ends).</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="home__microcopy">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
        <EmailSignup
          placeholder="you@domain.com"
          tag="home"
          submitText="Get notes"
        />
      </section>

      <section class="home__section home__links" data-section="links" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="6">
        <p class="home__kicker">LINKS</p>
        <SocialLinks />
      </section>

      <footer class="home__footer" data-section="footer" data-animate="fade-up" data-stagger="7">
        <p class="home__footer-text">
          <span class="home__footer-mark" data-logo="ch47">
            <Logo />
          </span>
          <span>Built by Jackson. 2026.</span>
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .home {
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    padding-block: max(var(--space-16), env(safe-area-inset-top, 0px) + var(--space-10))
      max(var(--space-16), env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px) + var(--space-10));
  }

  .home__container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: var(--padding-mobile);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .home__container {
      padding-inline: var(--padding-desktop);
    }
  }

  .home__hero {
    padding-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  .home__overline {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-fg-subtle);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6) 0;
  }

  .home__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 7vw, 4.25rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .home__subhead {
    margin: var(--space-6) 0 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fluid-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  .home__hero-cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .home__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 var(--space-6);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-fg-inverse);
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    text-decoration: none;
    width: fit-content;
    transition:
      background-color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out),
      transform var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out),
      box-shadow var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .home__cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px color-mix(in oklch, var(--color-accent) 20%, transparent);
  }

  .home__cta:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
    background: var(--color-accent-active);
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .home__cta:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-fg);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .home__cta-note {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fluid-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
  }

  .home__section {
    padding-block: var(--space-12);
  }

  .home__kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--color-fg-subtle);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6) 0;
  }

  .home__prose {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 68ch;
  }

  .home__prose p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fluid-md);
    line-height: var(--leading-prose);
    color: var(--color-fg);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .home__list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .home__list li {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fluid-md);
    line-height: var(--leading-prose);
    color: var(--color-fg);
  }

  .home__list li::marker {
    color: var(--color-fg-muted);
  }

  .home__feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .home__feature-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fluid-md);
    line-height: var(--leading-prose);
    color: var(--color-fg);
  }

  .home__feature-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-fg-muted);
  }

  .home__callout {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--color-bg-elevated) 75%, transparent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .home__callout p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .home__loop {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--color-bg-elevated) 75%, transparent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    max-width: fit-content;
  }

  .home__loop-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-fg-muted);
  }

  .home__loop-value {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .home__signup {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-14);
  }

  .home__signup-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fluid-xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0;
  }

  .home__signup-body {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--fluid-md);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-8) 0;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .home__signup-list {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6) 0;
  }

  .home__microcopy {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6) 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fluid-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-fg-subtle);
  }

  .home__links {
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
  }

  .home__footer {
    padding-block: var(--space-10) var(--space-4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .home__footer-mark {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .home__footer-text {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-fg-subtle);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
